item.title: I wanna live in los angelos
item.description: I am now in L.A. visiting my brother.. I have wrote the following entries on the road.. and thus they are out of order.. well they are in order.. but not entered seperatly. whatever.. here it goes.. So I just got done watching arlington road and part of edward scissorhands on the way to California. My laptop apparently had enough battery life to support almost 2 dvds. It rules. I am happy about that.
